imdb.plot outline: Leonard Maltin, one of the country's leading movie experts, gives REELZCHANNEL viewers his unique take on movies every week. Leonard reviews the latest movies in theaters, on DVD, On Demand and Pay Per View. Leonard will also reveal a hidden gem every week - a movie you might have missed that he thinks is worth your time. Leonard will give viewers the information they need to help them decide what movies to watch.
